## ğŸ“ˆ Model Architecture

| Layer Type | Units | Activation |
| ---------- | ----- | ---------- |
| Dense      | 6     | ReLU       |
| Dense      | 6     | ReLU       |
| Output     | 1     | Sigmoid    |

Loss: **binary_crossentropy**
Optimizer: **Adam**
